tosdr.case: This service tracks which web page referred you to it

title: This service tracks which web page referred you to it
quoteText:
Qwant also keeps other data related to your use of the services (associated for 7 days with a hash calculated from your IP address and the User Agent of your browser) including :

– The source of the user’s visit to the site (the HTTP referrer and the search field used to trigger the request);
